  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>패키지 전문 생산</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc1cc35a-3dcf-43ad-9886-fdd28bf26eb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/000.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">필로우 박스는 고급 크라프트로 만드세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>크라프트</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a57cec74-1276-4799-bc79-31936b65d833\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는 친환경 종이입니다. 가격대나 색깔 또는 앞, 뒷면 등 종류와 규격이 무척 다양합니다. 비싼 종이는 너무 비싸고 저렴한 종이는 붉은 갈색이 더 진해지는 특징이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-862cb30c-abcc-4b0f-940e-f92926d85026\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f2867372-09d8-46f8-b985-0b16bf61c04f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2aa5e3b0-1f13-4000-a466-d134f9d10005\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a50c2cd2-5563-4cd5-abfe-ed97a62c68d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">크라프트 종이는 여러 용도로 사용됩니다. 패키지로도 사용되고 주로 포장용 인쇄물에 활용이 많이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-24f946e2-1f50-4d2d-860f-fe70121649a2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:876px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce6b50ae-3837-4543-9e12-1ff9037504c8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-79bbff9b-d148-4775-80d9-8956453233db\" style=\"\">삼원페이퍼 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e53685bc-6cc5-4b91-9871-8e1def2f9ccb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9173a492-19f6-40cf-93c5-8a4dd323b209\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-5a19cd2f-9d82-4a1b-b83a-b14030bcef17\" style=\"\">삼원페이퍼 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6964026d-3da3-4962-8b8b-71d2e44af9d1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bbf8c612-f0c1-4ac0-bd15-08d94472e767\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-faecb5c9-b592-4b7d-af26-9c73d830654e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e7a447e7-9ccb-4e76-ae0f-76b25d7d890d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:811px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a0494bd-e4f2-4f22-9b58-762959c3cabd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-aec6503c-68b5-404d-9ac2-96fc29793d04\" style=\"\">두성종이 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18c4e2d7-c171-419d-8b06-2bd32de5ffa4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:802px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f7dd4788-c24d-44bf-ae6c-c0490acf139c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3faceac4-d5b5-450f-bda9-7b7d86e99934\" style=\"\">두성종이 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9bd6bb9f-3750-4714-8582-ca63e4d37a83\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7138f8d4-624c-4991-bebe-d1f24b0f0a0f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b399e40c-b4b7-46b6-8fa7-0a77b230df2a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">필로우(배게) 박스는 간단한 물건을 풍성하게(?) 포장하여 전달할 수 있는 용도로 제작됩니다. 제품의 무게는 무겁지 않고 패키지 박스 형태로 만들어지지 않고 포장용으로 전달하는 경우가 많습니다. 또한 필로우 박스는 네모 상자의 틀을 벗어나서 직접 전달하고 고객에게 독특한 포장용으로 인식할 수 있는 효과가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-733d45cc-5a83-4d1f-a812-8c00bef1eaa8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6cba5dc0-deae-4ec8-a044-5697634c9cc6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2afb6d7c-5bb4-4ae1-986b-221d56288a39\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d7870cf2-e0ac-429e-98f2-9de8899ecc6b\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">본 글을 작성할 수 있게 허락해 주신 관계자분께 감사의 말씀드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4713fb12-ce5c-4d42-9ccc-423cd3169910\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-351ea03d-ceb4-4ada-97e4-08f1e2bd148d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-ac594c0b-e5b1-425d-aac2-517bf9a04925\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ff5ef564-eb7d-4a9e-8027-259248d9cee5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9005f7ba-880c-4a35-a91d-68e6c445483d\" style=\"\">작업 일지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ada5260d-ef7f-43c0-93b2-20d85cc8862a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:672px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b5a2cc45-ba69-4b71-b693-84ddab792dff\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4af81e61-2aad-47e9-aa24-e9fc9e8807d8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-020077b7-c947-4f55-a08e-21cd781b03ea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">필로우 박스는 일단 기본적으로는 한 면만 접착합니다. 디자인 시 칼선은 다운로드를 하실 수 있습니다. 문의하시면 다운로드 사이트를 알려드립니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cbd403b5-ea2a-4298-8d24-97cafbee3adc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b83726f4-e6b1-4997-96cb-c9960c5117ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-84a249ac-bbfd-4dcc-9c59-71fb39810452\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2b75af8-d4f1-41b3-b9a8-718829cf85ff\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">현재 (주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트는 리뉴얼 중입니다. 랜딩 페이지 사이트로 변경 중이니 조금만 기다려 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6b117e61-8954-45db-b606-a3dffaf6f69c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7a580118-9e3e-401e-9e22-1c6402bc6d52\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3723265-13c1-4024-bb88-e326a7a3cba1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c41f8eb1-0dfb-4f28-8d82-b07218f5ab33\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이번 문의에서 가장 중요한 것은 종이의 선택이었습니다. 기존에 작업한 패키지가 뉴크라프트 보드지처럼 약간 붉은색이 들어가는 짙은 갈색이 마음에 안 든다는 요청이었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a2bcf4ae-4169-4cb6-93fa-60d3a2d7806c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:628px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-05c7a98e-7219-4405-b56b-b91a1c63c8f8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:556px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a2cc66f-70a8-4fe5-8926-7400d8cdb1d8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:663px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7112ca69-4eed-4914-abd0-54198846b1bb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-24efb5f1-ce53-4895-a352-4ef8f61e8d2c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a02ee265-90ec-47ea-99a4-3c36bfa0d790\" style=\"color:#555555;\">앞의 이미지도 말해주듯이 크라프트는 정말로 다양합니다. 짙은 암갈색부터 옅은 미색 같은 색상까지 여러 종류가 있습니다. 심지어 백색의 크라프트지도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a982b1d6-48fe-474d-86b1-614843f8947b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b84f4d3c-1fe7-494c-aa85-309cf0fa41dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f5cf1a14-2c97-4f1b-856a-7117b428194f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:678px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b5444c1a-2809-4433-af19-e39f3978aad6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a71c24a-8717-41e3-8cbb-a1e88a95e9e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d8d1cf31-531d-4278-a85a-1082b1163087\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지처럼 색상 차이가 심합니다. 진한 갈색을 선호하는 고객님도 분명히 있을 겁니다. 일단 종이를 결정해서 톡을 다시 주신다는 메시지셨습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-83f38c76-bfbb-4628-912f-10a48ec02ae6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-65c35604-8107-4a77-af31-709a30bba79c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-790739b4-5056-4db0-ab9c-2b56674df660\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8baa6338-71c5-4f87-9130-33eb73067a0c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 하루에 많은 문의가 들어옵니다. 하지만 한 분 한 분 소중한 인연이라고 생각하고 항상 견적이나 상담에 최선을 다하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b484a655-51a4-494a-808d-3714962ca9fd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bf5d2cbf-adca-480b-b177-d46fe3a51a42\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4ab29e02-9091-4ae1-b8a4-c9e6ac335822\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:675px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b7007a94-85b0-4cb2-83ee-82213385dba0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-339c9dfd-3d4f-4d0c-a302-d1974a1745fb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-77cd43f4-6a5d-449d-9d50-ac0e04db89a0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이의 결정과 진행에 대한 1차 구두 합의가 된 다음 데이터 검수를 진행했습니다. 물론 먹 1도 인쇄라 단순한 데이터였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce33e2a4-2410-4d1c-b9e9-953f74adc1b0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0dacc032-70bf-4597-ac0a-fda416d20dc3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ef09d0a3-8832-4c46-920a-f001a5294310\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:678px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-860932f5-7d63-4a8d-8b11-f37b8665c61b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ba317502-f5a9-4581-847a-4eb4866b1568\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d6c9d5f6-5cd7-47e2-9482-f90a88f395ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 고객님이 가장 많이 실수하시는 먹 K100 작업이 아닌 4도 혼용 색이 접수되었습니다. 수정해 작업해 드렸습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8016f456-a6a4-4170-8f23-c321b5a51f60\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bf602f11-df9b-41c8-804e-0e04bf7c7501\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-81eb0fea-9774-4574-a2eb-8b4f3715fd4d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a6189992-8ff9-4b26-85d7-852b275a9fb1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수량이 많고 종이가 비싼 종이라 일단 샘플 인쇄 진행을 했습니다. 당연히 사고가 나면 큰일 나니까요. 아무리 납기가 급해도 반드시 샘플 인쇄를 진행하고 본 작업을 실시하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-abfe7a7e-0f3c-48f2-875e-5d3c08dde3ab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:681px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/012.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-21323012-5814-4d61-a5cf-2f1f5b462423\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad8e15ef-0028-4eee-8848-2a3bfb0be1a1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6bc084b3-f25b-4cf2-8b85-b4f8f5abd83a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고개님께서 약간 로고를 작게 수정하신다고 해서 재 검수했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c7e582dc-9f55-482c-a338-b76b451844ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-502dae77-0d9a-4913-ac5a-5e9f33f73355\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-db5bf030-bda8-4a75-aabf-fc38c0618194\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1be95d7b-6b74-4b2d-9292-c3f299a73dc6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-153baba4-d324-49e2-9e9b-d7f8e06b1738\" style=\"\">톰슨(도무송) 작업 중</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-de43ff13-5dfd-45fc-ac79-00a8dfb7bd4f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-96a123b2-0199-4149-9b50-64f883580f23\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ae0c15f5-e132-430c-94ae-cb2d6059f316\" style=\"color:#555555;\">필로우 박스의 도무송 작업을 진행했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-32ab349c-8394-4706-8673-818513a37d4c\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a96dab47-ff21-457f-b89b-fe66315fa031\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-84656318-be5c-481a-8bff-8fc566da1b0e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0f78dbef-f5ce-408a-bf8c-d3280dbe4061\" style=\"color:#555555;\">톰슨(도무송)작업은 일단 목형을 제작합니다. 목형으로 칼을 만들고 그 칼이 종이를 눌러 따지거나 오시선, 미싱선 등이 작업됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-5bd2b9ff-0469-4c48-997b-65c57daa11b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-76c79eb0-e6be-4787-b24e-e33724a7605b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8ce10838-4851-49ef-a7c4-d186db056c2c\" style=\"\">(주)파파스컴퍼니의 약속</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b569a470-5586-4358-af1e-afea7fdebf59\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7913500c-3c6b-4d9a-b368-2c570a869922\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b06a1f92-8100-4063-9882-00f3cc25beb2\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>대량 주문의 경우 샘플을 무조건 미리 진행합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a316b7f-718f-4cbc-bce1-59fba83ebb44\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e5a11b75-070b-48c7-9a87-9ac98ec941c4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a97371e9-91c1-451d-b955-776ea8a89819\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-357d8f2a-2b01-4f22-8d9f-ad5026a40a01\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수량이나 금액의 큰 인쇄물 주문 시에는 사전에 샘플을 먼저 진행하여 확인 후 본 작업에 돌입하는 것을 원칙으로 합니다. 물론 100% 샘플 작업을 진행하는 것은 아닙니다. 하지만 거의 모든 작업을 미리 디지털 샘플 작업하여 사전에 검수를 진행하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4ecac7b6-df9d-4830-9dd5-1fd3f0863a51\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d22da284-d3f1-4bb2-805f-d1040b491c11\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56625e37-54ba-419a-babd-37c44112423e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c9cee0b-e6b8-419f-ba3b-1bca1e6083b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d723a2d1-22e1-4033-8846-94364dbf6869\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-70ed6fad-7ca0-4155-ad4d-b8cde286a349\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>디자인 데이터의 벨리데이션 체크 (인쇄 적합성 검사)를 진행합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-768f4354-e36e-4deb-ab44-ef5e78071218\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1d9efdc1-4543-4f04-954b-646837ffb60b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a0a19690-29ea-468b-b19e-d2cbf69a2362\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2dba6916-875e-4fdd-a797-cdad778347c2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">초보(?) 고객님의 데이터는 진행시 문제가 많이 발생됩니다. 에러의 경우의 수도 무척 다양하여 모든 부분을 다 설명드릴 수도 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1dfc19a3-13bd-45a4-ad01-edf61d0a172a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b292f5f7-8fd4-4f8d-8581-899e33b46758\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-36cd4bfb-64cc-4022-b16f-1731c7b37f0e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1213f2b-5fc6-4228-857b-411bef5136dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">어떤 종이는 박인쇄가 안되고 어떤 사이즈는 샘플을 만들 수 없을 만큼 크기에 제약사항이 있습니다. 거의 모든 디자이너가 알듯이 터짐 현상 방지를 위해 오시를 넣고 접어야 하며 코팅을 하면 안 되는 후공정도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e6c6995-4e92-4c89-8a86-733cf6529b8e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-785c961a-4e78-4ab1-9878-bdd98e77685b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0df77bd-441d-492f-8c2c-30b6e5288e3a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-49e841a9-cef6-48b3-aa58-10811543a15a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이렇듯이 인쇄의 에러 경우는 작업 전에 모르는 경우도 허다해서 30년 인쇄업을 한 저도 \"</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-06f444ba-b6cc-49bf-8ae9-5890f959ae46\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄는 어렵다!\"</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d2de63f-433d-41c1-8920-b461b7f461b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">라고 느낍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ecdcb77-05a1-4e81-a32e-8e3daba52094\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9466833f-e015-4030-b68c-5d785273a373\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fd36cd33-b4f3-4061-8a08-0ebbd1bf2572\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea8369ff-01d6-416a-a46a-2e5ed0048dc9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 데이터 검수에서 진행과정을 고객과 소통하면서 진행합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b19559c4-ba54-4a89-b16e-76cf695c7ab4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0984749-0cc1-4458-afd5-2e3d533bd933\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d9ded63f-051e-4ee9-bbc6-6ec881fd668b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-baa0c020-013e-4ef9-8b6e-44f9aad2f444\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cf833b55-3b08-4a81-8846-b4c5f6fbc622\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-be181028-b4d1-45fd-a630-891fe110f55e\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>고객과의 소통이 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 1등 목표입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-993a5e71-10fc-4988-9ab8-9f320a3bc428\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6c136df5-094d-4cb5-8792-209410b790d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2227808f-db6b-45ec-a5b8-c81f1b43c430\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a2d9145-ff39-414e-860d-0337c52bb9bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 견적요청, 디자인 검수를 1시간 이내에 반응(?) 해드리는 것을 목표로 합니다. 물론 죄송하게도 안되는 경우도 있지만 반드시 노력 중이라는 것을 알아주셨으면 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3d250e2c-1173-4134-9fbd-660731e061e2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a572a71-98d8-4fbd-a9f3-f77e01600553\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb81bd48-db6c-4270-9910-07aee8d2d64f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-617b89ce-8dd3-4b30-b0b0-6a5e87ebbd3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 진행 상황을 사진으로 보내드려서 안심하고 인쇄가 진행되는 것을 확인할 수 있도록 하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e7a60f4-4b3b-4293-b807-7ac4cd2b3b1f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56c0cbc1-58a2-4fed-a877-1e0d16fddad2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-7c5371df-e4a6-4a86-8bfb-14806eaf1b36\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e18c541-774f-4b20-b1a1-c896f5788029\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e0d01d2d-8b29-49dd-9d99-76b2eac3fcc5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-30e94e20-6307-4f17-a80a-5c383c6ec555\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니에게 요청하세요. 주문을 하지 않으셔도 좋습니다. 알아보시고 싶은 모든 인쇄물을 질문 주세요. 모든 인쇄물에 대한 요청을 가장 빠르게 알려드리도록 하겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc4d495b-3445-407c-9353-78d0f4366746\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223846972796/013.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-895f6903-2828-489e-9c59-f3e7fd2b8048\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-114c8ed3-7680-4b19-bb0e-6d9f975b9922\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56be56b0-6e5b-4069-8974-15582ac045d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}